Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest ls

Purpose:
  List archive objects.

Usage:
  spinedigest ls <archive.sdpub> [chapters|nodes|edges|evidence|fragments|summaries|meta] [--json]

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - JSON: yes.

Examples:
  spinedigest ls book.sdpub chapters
  spinedigest ls book.sdpub fragments --json
